data.description: Cute family home with a private back porch view of Ashland Creek Park, beautiful mature trees, the calming sound of Ashland Creek, and amazing sunsets!  So much room to park all your vehicles and toys!  Investors and Developers! Rare opportunity to develop .72 acre in Ashland City limit.  This property meets zoning requirements for lot-splitting.  Approval has been given by the City of Ashland for a total of 2 additional homes, possibly more.   Buyer to do their own due diligence in regard to zoning and lot split.  The existing home has walkability to Downtown and Lithia Park, also direct access to Ashland Creek Park.   Enjoy the serene melodies of Ashland Creek!  This 1,836sqft, 3Bdr/2Bath, 2-story home features 1 Bedroom and 1 Bathroom downstairs and the upper level has 2 Bedrooms and 1 Bath.   Recent updates include nicely remodeled upstairs bathroom and new vanity in downstairs bath.  Newer A/C unit and Gas Furnace, also new Water Heater in 2022.  Call for your showing today!
